<reference id="enum_recorderreasoncode">
    <title><ph keyref="RecorderReasonCode"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc">录制状态出错的原因。</ph></shortdesc>
    <refbody>
        <section id="parameters">
            <title>枚举值</title>
            <parml>
            <plentry>
                <pt><ph keyref="RECORDER_REASON_NONE"/></pt>
                <pd>0: 一切正常。</pd>
            </plentry>
            <plentry>
                <pt><ph keyref="RECORDER_ERROR_WRITE_FAILED"/></pt>
                <pd>1: 录制文件写入失败。</pd>
            </plentry>
            <plentry>
                <pt><ph keyref="RECORDER_ERROR_NO_STREAM"/></pt>
                <pd>2: 没有可录制的音视频流或者录制的音视频流中断超过 5 秒。</pd>
            </plentry>
            <plentry>
                <pt><ph keyref="RECORDER_ERROR_OVER_MAX_DURATION"/></pt>
                <pd>3: 录制时长超出上限。</pd>
            </plentry>
            <plentry>
                <pt><ph keyref="RECORDER_ERROR_CONFIG_CHANGED"/></pt>
                <pd>4: 录制配置改变。</pd>
            </plentry>
            </parml> </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>
